      "input": "Build me a dashboard for monitoring server health",
      "metadata": {
        "category": "dependency_handling",
        "notes": "Must follow dependency requirement, not re-route to web_builder",
        "system_prompt": "You are a Router specialist.\n\n**Dependency Requirement:**\nThe 'web_builder' specialist cannot proceed without artifacts from 'systems_architect'. Please route to 'systems_architect' next.\n\n(Note: Routing back to 'web_builder' before running 'systems_architect' will result in the same failure.)"
